page.title: 14A TYPICAL SATURDAY (CHILD)
page.content: I wake at 8:00am,I get up at 9:00am,I have breakfast and get ready (wash etc.).I watch T.V until 11:00am,then I do chores and jobs around the house until 12:00 noon when I write a bit of my book until 2:00pm, when we have lunch. I play outside until 4:30pm,when I take the dog for a walk.At 5:00pm I watch T.V. If Jamie and Andrew (My brothers)are in I have to watch{ {Wonder Woman,}if not I can watch the film on ITV.At 6:00pm I have tea,and finish watching the film.I watch T.V until 10:00pm when I usually go to bed.I read until 10:30pm when I go to sleep.
